          "Rival for Archbishop: A monstrous Tzimsce Elder from Peru."
        ],
        [
          "Elivira de Cordoba",
          "A Lasombra Elder, she now leads Cardine Scorso - one of the packs that assaulted the haven of the Lasombra Antediluvean"
        ],
        [
          "Kinyado",
          "An newly appointed Judge Inquiistor, he's here to help make sure the Black Hand does not gain too much power in San Diego"
        ],
